➜为什麼纸吸管总是插不进去？你可以这样做！
https://pansci.asia/archives/192159	18780
<ul><li>文／郭君逸 │国立台湾师范大学数学系副教授、魔术方块收藏家</li><li>本文转载自 UniMath《<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw">为什麼纸吸管总是插不进去，但塑胶吸管可以？</a>》</li></ul>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="560" height="373" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/59a4983de0a1a6791fabfee4fcf1b511-560x373.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192161" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/59a4983de0a1a6791fabfee4fcf1b511-560x373.png 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/59a4983de0a1a6791fabfee4fcf1b511-350x233.png 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/59a4983de0a1a6791fabfee4fcf1b511-768x511.png 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/59a4983de0a1a6791fabfee4fcf1b511-1536x1022.png 1536w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/59a4983de0a1a6791fabfee4fcf1b511.png 1645w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px" /><figcaption>图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<p>近几年国内环保意识抬头，因为塑胶吸管不能回收，造成大量的垃圾，所以环保署在&nbsp;2019&nbsp;年&nbsp;7&nbsp;月起禁用一次性塑胶吸管，不少饮料店纷纷改用成本高出许多的纸吸管，咖啡厅、餐厅则改用可重複清洗使用的金属吸管，金属吸管通常都是内用，直接放入杯中，不用插，所以还好……</p>
<h2>但纸吸管就常常让人觉得非常难用，插到烂掉还插不进去，为什麼呢？</h2>
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-style-default"><p>让我们从这些年吸管的演变开始说起。</p></blockquote>
<p>台湾的街头常常人手一杯手摇饮，珍珠奶茶更是红遍全球。在二十几年前，很多手摇饮料店的饮料杯就像现在麦当劳装可乐的杯子一样，是纸杯盖上塑胶盖，然后插「圆柱状」的吸管。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/69691c7bdcc3ce6d5d8a1361f22d04ac.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-192162" width="579" height="489" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/69691c7bdcc3ce6d5d8a1361f22d04ac.jpg 399w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/69691c7bdcc3ce6d5d8a1361f22d04ac-350x296.jpg 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/69691c7bdcc3ce6d5d8a1361f22d04ac-71x61.jpg 71w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/69691c7bdcc3ce6d5d8a1361f22d04ac-74x63.jpg 74w" sizes="(max-width: 579px) 100vw, 579px" /><figcaption>图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<p>直到叶益芳先生发明了封口机后，手摇饮逐渐换成如今常见的封口杯，随意放置饮料也不会流出来，非常方便。全面换成封口杯之后，有一样东西也跟着产生微妙变化，那就是「吸管」。</p><div class="pansc-content"></ins>
<script async type="text/javascript" src="//cdn.holmesmind.com/js/init.js"></script></div>
<h2>吸管的一端必须变尖，方便直接插穿杯子的封口膜。</h2>
<p>笔者前几天买了一杯珍奶，结果吸管都插烂了还插不进去，加上天气炎热，火气一上来索性就不喝了，满脑子一直在想「为什麼吸管越来越难插」，直到我发现原因写完这篇文章，珍奶就这样放在研究室的桌上还没喝，应该已经坏了……</p>
<p>高中的时候大家可能都学过二次曲线，虽然课程内容着重在代数上的运算，大部份老师或多或少还是会提一下古典几何中的圆锥截痕，或称圆锥曲线，例如下图展示平面在双圆锥上产生的各种截痕。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/d54b7ba27571a2f00b38ed9273b974f2.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192163" width="562" height="375" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/d54b7ba27571a2f00b38ed9273b974f2.png 400w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/d54b7ba27571a2f00b38ed9273b974f2-350x234.png 350w" sizes="(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px" /><figcaption>平面在双圆锥上产生的截痕。图／<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Conic_sections_with_plane.svg#/media/File:Conic_sections_with_plane.svg">Wikimedia</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<p>当双圆锥退化成圆柱，此时的截痕就会变成这样，看起来有点像一根吸管被切了一刀。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/fe47aa7c733c490d36e80508d5dc4019.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192164" width="264" height="268"/><figcaption>平面在圆柱上产生的截痕。图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<h2><strong>但是，你手中的吸管真的长这样吗？</strong></h2>
<p>这裡先考考大家，吸管从侧面看过去，长相会是下列哪一个图？</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/da89e38d2085d08a94af46c0706b4cae-560x129.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192165" width="624" height="144" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/da89e38d2085d08a94af46c0706b4cae-560x129.png 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/da89e38d2085d08a94af46c0706b4cae-350x80.png 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/da89e38d2085d08a94af46c0706b4cae-768x176.png 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/da89e38d2085d08a94af46c0706b4cae.png 784w" sizes="(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px" /><figcaption>图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<p><strong>答案是</strong> D！</p>
<p>什麼！！！怎麼跟圆锥截痕不一样？！</p>
<p><strong>因为…吸管就不是圆锥截痕啊！吸管就不是圆锥截痕啊！吸管就不是圆锥截痕啊！</strong></p>
<p>答案违背我们直觉的原因在于，吸管用剪刀剪或用裁刀裁切时，吸管会先被刀压扁，然后才直直剪过去，最后吸管的弹性，会再让它弹回来形成<strong>空心柱体</strong>。</p>
<h2>用数学来看吸管&nbsp;</h2>
<p>剪裁前的吸管本身是圆柱（设半径为&nbsp;1 ），将之直立于&nbsp;xy-平面利用参数式来描述吸管截痕曲线的话，它会是</p>
<p><strong>r</strong>(t) = &lt;cos t, sin t, z(t)&gt;</p>
<p>这种形式，t 是绕圆的角度，观察重点在于高度&nbsp;z&nbsp;是多少了。若是圆柱截痕，截平面&nbsp;45&nbsp;度切下去的话，即是用平面&nbsp;z=x&nbsp;来切，此时&nbsp;<strong>r</strong>(t) = &lt;cos t, sin t, cost&gt;。调整&nbsp;t&nbsp;的范围，可以画出下面的&nbsp;3D&nbsp;图。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/96a3be3cf272e017046d1b2674a52bd3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192166" width="339" height="231"/><figcaption>图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<p>但问题在于剪吸管时，吸管会先被剪刀压扁，再沿&nbsp;z=x&nbsp;剪过去，也就是 z 随着 x 等比例增加，然后吸管再弹回，此时就好像将这张压扁的纸贴在圆柱上，换句话说在固定一个高度 z 时吸管回复至圆形的状态，亦即圆参数式中的角度随着 z(t) = t 做变化，所以截面曲线就是&nbsp;<strong>r</strong>(t) = &lt;cos t, sin t, t&gt;，画出来的3D&nbsp;吸管如下图。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/a2ef406e2c2351e0b9e80029c909242d-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192167" width="578" height="305" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/a2ef406e2c2351e0b9e80029c909242d-1.png 400w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/a2ef406e2c2351e0b9e80029c909242d-1-350x185.png 350w" sizes="(max-width: 578px) 100vw, 578px" /><figcaption>图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<p>从吸管的侧面看过去，相当于投影在&nbsp;xz-平面，即为&nbsp;z=cos<sup>-1</sup>&nbsp;x&nbsp;的图形。吸管横摆也可以说成&nbsp;z=cos x&nbsp;或&nbsp;z=sin x&nbsp;週期函数中的一部分。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/4d00d79b6733c9cc066584a02ed03410-560x183.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192168" width="582" height="190" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/4d00d79b6733c9cc066584a02ed03410-560x183.png 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/4d00d79b6733c9cc066584a02ed03410-350x115.png 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/4d00d79b6733c9cc066584a02ed03410.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 582px) 100vw, 582px" /><figcaption>图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<h2><strong>你知道大多数吸管并不是切&nbsp;45&nbsp;度吗？</strong></h2>
<p>因为这样切最后会剩太多饮料吸不起来，造成浪费。一般会介于&nbsp;25&nbsp;度至&nbsp;40&nbsp;度之间较恰当。例如下图中吸管大约是切&nbsp;37&nbsp;度左右。若将吸管直着摆，尖端从侧面看，斜率最大，所以<strong>插吸管时，应该要垂直插最省力</strong>。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/e45ee7ce7e88149af8dd32b27f9512ce-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192169" width="308" height="447"/><figcaption>图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<p>很多人将原因归咎于纸製吸管比较软，然而真相恐怕并非如此。纸浸了水后的确会变软，但还没插进杯裡的纸吸管其实是硬的，甚至比塑胶吸管硬多了。</p>
<p>最主要的原因还是在于<strong>形状</strong>，纸吸管的切面是椭圆，而不像塑胶吸管一样有个尖尾。</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/25b2916b5c49db617f52fa5ea48efee7-16.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-192170" width="292" height="389"/><figcaption>纸吸管经常插到烂掉都插不进去。图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
<h2><strong>为什麼纸吸管的切面是椭圆形呢？</strong></h2>
<p>相较于塑胶，纸的弹性没那麼大，被裁刀重重一压就扁了，回复不了圆柱状，除了造型不好看，恐怕压扁的吸管也不好用。因此，纸吸管的生产过程是在不变形的情况下锯断，或是使用雷射切割，故其截面接近我们课本所说的椭圆。<strong>因为没有「尖端」，所以非常难插。</strong></p>
<h2>所以纸吸管到底要怎麼用才好？</h2>
<p>在此有个小建议，读者以后拿到纸吸管，先不要急着插，先用剪刀剪一下，就会好插很多；而使用纸吸管的饮料店，也可以在柜枱准备把剪刀和<strong>方格纸</strong>，平时没事剪剪吸管<strong>顺便画三角函数</strong>，要卫生一点的话就让顾客自己剪，方便、省钱、环保还可以学数学，可说是一举数得啊！</p>
<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="560" height="312" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b-4-560x312.png" alt="" class="wp-image-192171" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b-4-560x312.png 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b-4-350x195.png 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b-4-768x428.png 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b-4-1536x855.png 1536w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b-4.png 1895w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px" /><figcaption>&nbsp;纸吸管剪一下也可以轻鬆插入。图／<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/g2.nctu.edu.tw/unimath/2020-08/straw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UniMath</a></figcaption></figure></div>
